page.title: 14SUPERNATURAL
page.content: During a normal workin day, in an old factory which had recently been occupied by a new firm there was a strange occurence. In a back room a pile of heavy boxes had been carefully stacked.The workmen closed the door to the room and settled down to a well earned lunch-break. As they were eating they heard a shuffling noise from the room and then a series of crashes. On investigation the boxes were littered about the room. There was noone in the room at the time. This occured three times during one shift. Although the factory is still used, this room is no longer in use. Things have been quiet since.
